-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

ControlGeek Server is designed to be used with pigpiod on the Raspberry Pi.
ControlGeek Server does not distribute pigpiod; the following is provided for
informational purposes only.

The original source code of pigpiod may be found at

    <http://abyz.co.uk/rpi/pigpio/download.html>

pigpiod is free and unencumbered software released into the public domain. For
details see <http://unlicense.org/>.

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

ControlGeek Server bundles the Sans and Sans-Bold forms of the Noto Font
family. Those fonts may be found at

    <https://github.com/googlei18n/noto-fonts>.

The license for Noto Fonts is as follows.

    This Font Software is licensed under the SIL Open Font License,
    Version 1.1.

The SIL Open Font License is available at <http://scripts.sil.org/OFL>
